This paper deals with wireless communication and networking, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The paper also discusses the optimization of the system, which can be categorized under Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper involves signal processing and modulation techniques, which can be classified under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR).
